dmca_clarifications: I am (Rajwinder Singh Brar) the director of RBSEO Ltd.  
Company based in UK. Google has stopped our website homepage  
www.rbseo.co.uk from indexing in Google database. We have not received any  
information on our company email address or Google webmaster tool about the  
copyright infringing. I am taking the full responsibility that our contents  
are original and are not copied from anywhere, any website or any  
organisation and we are not using any black hat techniques for SEO purposes.

I would humbly request Google to re-instate our website www.rbseo.co.uk  
homepage in Google database. Should you require further information  
regarding this matter?
Please feel free to contact me on +44 (0) 7988741208 or info@rbseo.co.uk
